text: This transmits obsolete IRM 3.30.28, Work Planning and Control, Individual Review

IRM 3.30.28 is obsolete because quality review data previously recorded in the Automated 3926 System is now collected in the Embedded Quality Submission Processing (EQSP) System. Relevant material from IRM 3.30.28 is included in IRM 3.30.30, Embedded Quality for Submission Processing, including: Quality review objectives and reviewer requirements, managementâ€™s role and responsibilities, individual review sampling guidelines, and individual review procedures.
